dct_title_s: Park View Estates, New Brunswick, New Jersey verso
dct_description_sm: Verso of street map of Park View Estates, New Brunswick is promotional pamphlet for the newly constructed Park View Estates residential development along Easton Avenue and Franklin Boulevard. Includes information about purchase pricing, model home tours and local recreational areas. Drawn illustration and four photographic illustrations.
